Media personality Bonang Matheba's ‘brand new book is finally’ here! Bonang took to Twitter just a few hours ago to announce that her book is now available for pre-ordering. The Top billing star took a snap of the cover, with the caption”....years in the making! Finally my brand new book, From A to B is now available for pre-order.... @ExclusiveBooks” The book unfolds the journey of a little girl who grew up in Mafikeng in North West and now finds her face alongside, international star Halle Berry, in a worldwide Revlon campaign. In her book, Matheba shares some of the most  important lessons in life. Her journey that saw her become a successful businesswoman, brand ambassador and television personality. The book will take readers into Matheba's life that is not public knowledge. Fans started celebrating the arrival of this long awaited book: 